snippet: Mike Westhoff, the special-teams coach whose players are usually among the league’s best, has not lost his determination.
abstract: New York Jets special teams coach Mike Westhoff, whose players are usually among league’s best, has not lost his determination despite unit's poor performance this season.
lead_paragraph: Mike Westhoff, the special-teams coach whose players are usually among the league’s best, has not lost his determination.

headline.seo: Jets’ Miscues on Special Teams Keep Mike Westhoff Up at Night
headline.main: Miscues Lead a Jets Coach to Lose Sleep, Not Resolve
